e bank specializes in residential mortgage lending as of december   trustco banks assets were  billion trustco bank has paid dividends to its shareholders for over  consecutive years and has remained profitable throughout its history including the recent financial crisis in may  snl financial rated trustco bank the th best performing savings bank in the country trustco bank is traded on the nasdaq under trst current interest rates view rates    about us employment opportunities employment listings we are trustco bank a letter from our president  ceo the history of trustco bank trustco banks home town heroes investor relations checking  savings home town checking savings accounts money market accounts certificates of deposit cds retirement accounts mortgages purchase refinance new construction home equity start mortgage application submit mortgage inquiry pending web app login online banking online banking login estatements security and fraud prevention fraud prevention alerts mobile banking information financial services estate settlement investment management account retirement plans  rollovers trust under your will financial planning living trust fixed annuities calculators customer service branch  atm locator contact us privacy policy sitemap  copyright 7 trustco bank all rights reserved equal housing lender member fdic nmls identifier 77 nmls consumer access  verify a financial service provider here » website development and vsite™ content management by es trustco bank  personal loan products  new york florida massachusetts new jersey vermont online banking contact us  find atms  branches 7 search site submit menu home personal deposit accounts » home town checking savings accounts money market accounts certificates of deposit cds retirement accounts loan products » mortgages » hometown first time home buyers program mortgage loan calculator home equity loans and credit lines consumer loans auto loans auto loan calculator student loans building loans trustco hom